OL,5,G1615 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FArgentina v Egypt (Kick-off
OL,7,     F5.00pm). Coverage of the seventh
OL,8,     Fround-of-16 match, which takes
OL,9,     Fplace at Atlanta Stadium in the
OL,10,     FUSA. Argentina were involved a
OL,11,     Fremarkable last-16 match, edging
OL,12,     Fpast minnows Cape Verde 3-2 after
OL,13,     Fextra-time, with the tournament
OL,14,     Fdebutantes making sure they would
OL,15,     Fbe remembered as one of the
OL,16,     Fhighlights of these finals. Egypt
OL,17,     Fneeded a penalty shootout to beat
OL,18,     FAustralia in the last round,
OL,19,     Fbreaking new ground by winning a
OL,20,     FWorld Cup finals knockout match
OL,21,     Ffor the first time
