OL,5,G2015 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FSwitzerland v Colombia (Kick-off
OL,7,     F9.00pm). Coverage of the eighth
OL,8,     Fround-of-16 match, which takes
OL,9,     Fplace at BC Place Vancouver in
OL,10,     FCanada. Switzerland had a game to
OL,11,     Fforget at the corresponding stage
OL,12,     Fof the 2022 World Cup when they
OL,13,     Fwere thrashed 6-1 by Portugal.
OL,14,     FHowever, they will be hopeful of a
OL,15,     Fmuch stronger showing this time
OL,16,     Faround, having topped a group
OL,17,     Fcontaining Canada, Bosnia and
OL,18,     FHerzegovina and Qatar, before
OL,19,     Feasing past Algeria 2-0 in the
OL,20,     Fround of 32. Colombia have only
OL,21,     Fscored five goals in their four
OL,22,     Fmatches, but that was enough for
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
