OL,5,G2335 The Assembly
OL,6,     FStephen Fry faces a grilling from
OL,7,     Fa cast of autistic and
OL,8,     Flearning-disabled interviewers.
OL,9,     FDid he take drugs in Buckingham
OL,10,     FPalace? Is he happy to be alive?
OL,11,     FAs the questions come thick and
OL,12,     Ffast, Stephen opens up about
OL,13,     Fmental health, shame and
OL,14,     Fself-criticism. There are probing
OL,15,     Fquestions about love, identity and
OL,16,     Fbelief, alongside moments of pure
OL,17,     Fmischief and laughter - including
OL,18,     Fan explosive question about his
OL,19,     Fsexual preferences
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
